opinions.text:
ORDER
The plaintiff’s motion to dismiss this appeal is denied without prejudice to plaintiff’s filing a proper motion with an adequate supporting memorandum.

attorneys: Dennis S. Baluch, Providence, for plaintiff.
Donald E. Allcock, Pawtucket, for defendant.
